title: Top Places to visit in Uttar Dinajpur, Raiganj, West Bengal
content: Uttar Dinajpur is a district of the Indian state of West Bengal. Created on 1 April 1992 by the division of the erstwhile West Dinajpur district, it comprises two subdivisions: Raiganj and Islampur.
